member.example:
    The following example demonstrates how to programmatically set the Orientation 
    property of a RadProgressBar control.
    
		void Page_Load(object sender, EventArgs e)
		{
			RadProgressBar myProgressBar = new RadProgressBar();
			myProgressBar.Orientation = Orientation.Vertical;
		}

